title: Cedar Ave S - 1 BR
posting_body: ['This building offers clean, quiet, one-bedroom units with long-term tenants.', ' Well-maintained, the building is close to parks and public transit options.', '3848 Cedar Av S, Minneapolis MN 55407', '1 Bedroom', 'Hardwood floors throughout', 'Living room, dining room, kitchen, bedroom and bath.', 'Lots of closet space', 'On-site Laundry and extra storage in basement.', 'On bus route (Cedar Ave) and 4 blocks from Bloomington Ave', 'Rent - $900/month', 'Heat and water/waste included', 'Gas for stove and electricity - responsibility of the tenant', "Deposit - 1 month's rent ($900)", 'Available August 1.', 'Text today to schedule a showing', 'Wayne', 'show contact info']
